snippet.title: Hellpoint Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
http://playhellpoint.com / https://store.steampowered.com/app/628670/Hellpoint/

Hellpoint is a dark sci fi action RPG set in the aftermath of a massive quantic cataclysm. You play as a mysterious ghoulish character whose intentions are entirely determined by your decisions.
